comment: @Itsjoeco That's so anti capitalist to say
Friend opened a face mask factory, production capacity of 1.5 million mask per day https://t.co/fuIAo6bsJJ
High prices lead to higher production, now where have I heard that before? ? https://t.co/0ubUhjnFtz

Scarcity of needed supplies is the real scourge, not inflation.  We already have a system, the market, that is simple to administer and efficiently routes supplies to buyers. We shouldn't trade it for one that is incredibly complex to administer and does a much worse job.
